data.description: Definitely one of a kind Lake Mitchell home you will fall in love with the minute you step in sunroom.  Bright, airy vaulted wood ceiling, high windows showing off the impressive water view. Walk into joining great room/dining/kitchen and you will not want to leave.  Stone fireplace; wood ceilings; custom kitchen cabinets; more views of lake; a very comfortable home with so much to offer. Master bedroom and bath located on first floor.  Den; 2 bedrooms; full bath; and laundry room on bottom floor. More open views of lake and walk out door to covered patio with grill area and outdoor kitchen. Workshop; carport area and enclosed boathouse enhance this further enhance this property. New 24 x 40 shop with lean to sheds on both sides ; concrete floor; power; water;roll up doors and walk in door is excellent for boat storage; mowers and workshop.He shed!!!  Price to sell so dont wait to view.  Set appointment today. Best locations for firework show and parades . Cargle area on LAKE MITCHELL
